					<div class="comment-metadata">
						<a href="https://mastransky.wordpress.com/2021/01/10/firefox-were-finally-getting-hw-acceleration-on-linux/#comment-15862"><time datetime="2021-03-17T09:13:58+00:00">March 17, 2021 at 9:13 am</time></a>					</div><!-- .comment-metadata -->

